## Integration Test (Testcontainers)
```csharp
public class OrderApiTests : IClassFixture<WebApplicationFactory<Program>>
{
    private readonly HttpClient _client;

    public OrderApiTests(WebApplicationFactory<Program> factory)
    {
        _client = factory.WithWebHostBuilder(builder =>
        {
            builder.ConfigureServices(services =>
            {
                // Testcontainers ile gercek SQL Server
                services.RemoveAll<DbContextOptions<AppDbContext>>();
                services.AddDbContext<AppDbContext>(o => o.UseSqlServer(_sqlContainer.GetConnectionString()));
            });
        }).CreateClient();
    }

    [Fact]
    public async Task CreateOrder_ValidRequest_Returns201()
    {
        var response = await _client.PostAsJsonAsync("/api/v1/orders", new { ... });
        Assert.Equal(HttpStatusCode.Created, response.StatusCode);
    }

    [Fact]
    public async Task GetOrder_WrongTenant_Returns404()
    {
        // Cross-tenant isolation testi
        _client.DefaultRequestHeaders.Authorization = new("Bearer", tenantBToken);
        var response = await _client.GetAsync($"/api/v1/orders/{tenantAOrderId}");
        Assert.Equal(HttpStatusCode.NotFound, response.StatusCode);
    }
}
```

## Contract Testing (Pact)
```
Amac: Frontend-Backend API kontratini dogrula
├── Consumer (Frontend): "Bu endpoint'e su request gonderirsem, su response bekliyorum"
├── Provider (Backend): "Evet, ben bu kontrata uyuyorum"
├── Pact Broker: kontrat dosyalarini sakla ve paylas
├── CI'da: her PR'da kontrat dogrulama
```

## E2E Test (Playwright)
```typescript
test('user can create order', async ({ page }) => {
  await page.goto('/orders/new');
  await page.fill('[data-testid="customer-select"]', 'ABC Corp');
  await page.click('[data-testid="add-item-btn"]');
  await page.fill('[data-testid="quantity-input"]', '10');
  await page.click('[data-testid="submit-btn"]');
  await expect(page.locator('[data-testid="success-message"]')).toBeVisible();
  await expect(page).toHaveURL(/\/orders\/[a-z0-9-]+/);
});
```

## Frontend Test (Vitest)
```typescript
import { render, screen, waitFor } from '@testing-library/react';
import userEvent from '@testing-library/user-event';

test('shows validation error for empty name', async () => {
  render(<ItemForm onSubmit={vi.fn()} />);
  await userEvent.click(screen.getByRole('button', { name: /save/i }));
  await waitFor(() => {
    expect(screen.getByText(/name is required/i)).toBeInTheDocument();
  });
});
```

## Mutation Testing (Stryker)
```
Amac: Testlerin kalitesini olc (sadece coverage yetmez)
├── Mutant: kodda kucuk degisiklik (> yerine <, true yerine false)
├── Killed: test basarisiz oldu = iyi test ✅
├── Survived: test hala gecti = zayif test 🔴
├── Hedef: Mutation score > %80
```

## Flaky Test Yonetimi
```
Tespit:
├── CI'da 3+ kez calis, farkli sonuc = flaky
├── Quarantine: flaky testi ayri suite'e tasi
├── Fix: race condition, timing, shared state, external dependency

Onleme:
├── Deterministic test data (fake/builder, ASLA random)
├── Isolated DB per test class (Testcontainers)
├── Clock abstraction (IDateTimeProvider)
├── Retry ASLA cozum — root cause bul
```

